<a href='/media-center/news/press-releases/2016/06/09/johnson-controls-to-build-4th-automotive-battery-plant-in-china' onclick='' target='_self' >Johnson Controls to build 4th battery plant in China</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="overlay-text">
                            Johnson Controls is forming a joint venture with Binzhou Bohai Piston Co., Ltd., to build its fourth Chinese automotive battery manufacturing plant. Aimed at serving both automakers and aftermarket customers, the facility will be located in Binzhou, Shandong Province.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item ">

                        <div class="social">

                            <div class="social-title">
<a href='/media-center/news/press-releases/2016/05/26/johnson-controls-announces-research-partnership-at-the-university-of-wisconsinmadison' onclick='' target='_self' >Next-gen battery-electric vehicles</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="overlay-text">
                            Johnson Controls has announced two multi-year research projects at the University of Wisconsin&ndash;Madison aimed at enhancing the fuel efficiency of start-stop and next-generation battery-electric vehicles.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item ">

                        <div class="social">

                            <div class="social-title">
<a href='/insights/2016/ps/features/40-years-of-battery-manufacturing-celebrated-at-guardamar' onclick='' target='_self' >40 years of battery production</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="overlay-text">
                            The Johnson Controls plant in Guardamar, which specializes in the production of VARTA&reg; car batteries, celebrated its 40 years anniversary with employees and politicians on May 4.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item ">

                        <div class="social">

                            <div class="social-title">
<a href='/media-center/news/press-releases/2016/04/19/make-an-impact-this-earth-day-and-recycle-your-vehicles-old-battery' onclick='' >Recycle your battery</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="overlay-text">
                            To help consumers find a nearby facility to recycle used vehicle, boat, motorcycle or lawn/garden batteries, Johnson Controls, the world&rsquo;s largest manufacturer and recycler of vehicle batteries, is encouraging consumers to visit its website www.recyclingmybattery.com.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item ">

                        <div class="social">

                            <div class="social-title">
<a href='/en_latinamerica/insights/2016/ps/features/varta-wins-awards' onclick='' >Top awards for VARTAÂ® batteries</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="overlay-text">
                            Johnson Controls automotive battery brand VARTA&reg; was honored in China for its advanced technology and environmental performance.
                        </div>
